<p class="ql-align-center">长沙市公安局雨花分局</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黎托派出所指导员杨志争</strong>闻讯后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">带领<strong>辅警曹凌</strong>迅速赶到现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随即赶来的还有<strong>消防队员</strong></p>
